  <summary date="2015-05-01T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Municipal Bond Market Support Act of 2015

Amends Internal Revenue Code provisions relating to the small issuer exemption from interest expense allocation rules for financial institutions to: (1) permanently increase from $10 million to $30 million the annual limit on the amount of tax-exempt obligations that a small issuer may issue, and (2) allow an inflation adjustment to such increased limit amount after 2015.</summary>
